graph TD
    A[User Input] --> B[Firewall Node: Input Sanitizer]
    
    subgraph Security Layer
    B --> C{Detects Malicious Patterns?}
    end
    
    C -->|Yes: Injection Attempt| D[Denial Node]
    C -->|No: Safe Prompt| E[Core Agent / LLM]
    
    subgraph Execution Layer
    E -->|Generates Response| F[Validation Node: PII Scanner]
    F --> G{Contains Sensitive Data?}
    end
    
    G -->|Yes: SSN/Credit Card found| H[Redaction Node]
    G -->|No: Clean Output| I[Final Secure Response]
    
    D -->|Canned Message| I
    H --> I
